Allow permission groups to be referred to by name and auto-resolve their IDs in the AccountApiToken resource.

```ts
const accountAccessToken = await AccountApiToken("account-access-token", {
  name: "alchemy-account-access-token",
  policies: [
    {
      effect: "allow",
      permissionGroups: ["Workers R2 Storage Write"],
      resources: {
        "com.cloudflare.api.account": "*",
      },
    },
  ],
});
```

# schema: New schema for `real-estate.lease-agreement`

## Schema Action
New Schema

## Schema Motivation
Adding a schema for structured extraction of lease agreements, supporting both commercial and residential lease documents.

Benefits:
- Standardizes lease agreement data extraction
- Captures comprehensive lease terms and conditions
- Flexible structure for different lease types

## Sample Document
[Sample Commercial Lease Agreement](https://storage.googleapis.com/sample-hub-data/real-estate.lease-agreement/sample_lease_doc_6.pdf)

